high_descs: Move forward past the toilet on the left and move to the black table between the door and the bathtub.
Pick up the green spray bottle closest to the candle on the right side from the table.
Turn around, move past the bathtub until you reach the sink, then turn to the right and face the toilet.
Place the green dispenser bottle on top of the toilet cistern to the right of the purple pump bottle above the toilet handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle on the toilet cistern.

high_descs: Put the bottle on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the spray bottle on the toilet
